solution: ```class Solution {
    public int findMaxK(int[] nums) {
        boolean[] seen = new boolean[1001];
        int max = -1;
        for (int n : nums) {
            if (n > 0) seen[n] = true;
        }
        for (int n : nums) {
            if (n < 0 && seen[-n]) max = Math.max(max, -n);
        }
        return max;
    }
}
